e.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa Mga Pangunahing Punto (Key Takeaways) na, \'Ang pag-iwas ay palaging mas mahusay kaysa sa pagtugon sa emerhensiya.\'","choice_a_en":"Recovery","choice_a_fil":"Pagbawi (Recovery)","choice_b_en":"Investigation","choice_b_fil":"Imbestigasyon","choice_c_en":"Prevention","choice_c_fil":"Pag-iwas (Prevention)","choice_d_en":"Evacuation","choice_d_fil":"Paglikas (Evacuation)"},{"number":15,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Who should repair faulty wiring according to electrical safety best practices?","question_fil":"Sino ang dapat mag-ayos ng sirang wiring ayon sa pinakamahusay na kasanayan sa kaligtasan sa kuryente?","explanation_en":"The lesson advises, \'Have faulty wiring repaired by a qualified electrician.\'","explanation_fil":"Pinapayuhan ng aralin na, \'Ipinaayos ang sirang wiring sa isang kwalipikadong electrician.\'","choice_a_en":"Anyone with basic tools","choice_a_fil":"Sinuman na may pangunahing kasangkapan","choice_b_en":"The homeowner or resident","choice_b_fil":"Ang may-ari ng bahay o residente","choice_c_en":"A qualified electrician","choice_c_fil":"Isang kwalipikadong electrician","choice_d_en":"A general handyman without specific electrical certification","choice_d_fil":"Isang pangkalahatang handyman na walang partikular na sertipikasyon sa kuryente"},{"number":16,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"What is a recommended practice after cooking with gas?","question_fil":"Ano ang inirerekomendang kasanayan pagkatapos magluto gamit ang gas?","explanation_en":"The lesson states, \'Turn off gas valves after cooking.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin na, \'Patayin ang mga gas valve pagkatapos magluto.\'","choice_a_en":"Leave gas valves open for ventilation","choice_a_fil":"Iwanan ang mga gas valve na nakabukas para sa bentilasyon","choice_b_en":"Turn off gas valves","choice_b_fil":"Patayin ang mga gas valve","choice_c_en":"Store flammable liquids near 