	(6, 6, 1, 'published', '[{"number":1,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"According to the lesson, what is the primary purpose of fire extinguishers?","question_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, ano ang pangunahing layunin ng mga fire extinguisher?","explanation_en":"The lesson overview states, \'Fire extinguishers are one of the most important pieces of emergency equipment used to control small fires before they become uncontrollable.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa pangkalahatang-ideya ng aralin, \'Ang mga fire extinguisher ay isa sa pinakamahalagang kagamitan pang-emerhensiya na ginagamit upang kontrolin ang maliliit na sunog bago ito lumaki at hindi na makontrol.\'","choice_a_en":"To extinguish all types of fires, regardless of size.","choice_a_fil":"Upang apulahin ang lahat ng uri ng sunog, anuman ang laki.","choice_b_en":"To control small fires before they become uncontrollable.","choice_b_fil":"Upang kontrolin ang maliliit na sunog bago ito lumaki at hindi na makontrol.","choice_c_en":"To provide a temporary barrier against spreading flames.","choice_c_fil":"Upang magbigay ng pansamantalang harang laban sa lumalaganap na apoy.","choice_d_en":"To alert emergency services to a fire incident.","choice_d_fil":"Upang alertuhin ang mga serbisyo ng emerhensiya tungkol sa insidente ng sunog."},{"number":2,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which type of fire extinguisher is specifically NOT recommended for use on electrical fires or flammable liquid fires?","question_fil":"Aling uri ng fire extinguisher ang partikular na HINDI inirerekomenda para gamitin sa sunog na dulot ng kuryente o sa sunog ng mga nasusunog na likido?","explanation_en":"The lesson content specifies for Water Fire Extinguishers: \'Do NOT use on electrical or flammable liquid fires.\'","explanation_fil":"Ang nilalaman ng aralin ay partikular na nagsasaad para sa mga Water Fire Extinguisher: \'HUWAG gamitin sa sunog na dulot ng kuryente o sa sunog ng mga nasusunog na likido.\'","choice_a_en":"Dry Chemical Powder (ABC)","choice_a_fil":"Dry Chemical Powder (ABC)","choice_b_en":"Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082)","choice_b_fil":"Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082)","choice_c_en":"Water Fire Extinguisher","choice_c_fil":"Water Fire Extinguisher","choice_d_en":"Foam Fire Extinguisher","choice_d_fil":"Foam Fire Extinguisher"},{"number":3,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"A Dry Chemical Powder (ABC) extinguisher is commonly found in various facilities because it is suitable for which fire types?","question_fil":"Ang Dry Chemical Powder (ABC) extinguisher ay karaniwang makikita sa iba\'t ibang pasilidad dahil ito ay angkop para sa anong uri ng sunog?","explanation_en":"The lesson states that Dry Chemical Powder (ABC) is \'Suitable for: Class A, Class B, Class C.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, ang Dry Chemical Powder (ABC) ay \'Angkop para sa: Class A, Class B, Class C na sunog.\'","choice_a_en":"Class A and Class B fires only.","choice_a_fil":"Sunog ng Class A at Class B lamang.","choice_b_en":"Class B and Class C fires only.","choice_b_fil":"Sunog ng Class B at Class C lamang.","choice_c_en":"Class A, Class B, and Class C fires.","choice_c_fil":"Sunog ng Class A, Class B, at Class C.","choice_d_en":"Electrical and flammable liquid fires only.","choice_d_fil":"Sunog na dulot ng kuryente at nasusunog na likido lamang."},{"number":4,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"Which fire extinguisher type is ideal for protecting computers and server rooms because it leaves no residue?","question_fil":"Aling uri ng fire extinguisher ang perpekto para sa pagprotekta sa mga computer at server room dahil wala itong iniiwan na residue?","explanation_en":"The lesson states that Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082) \'Leaves no residue, making it ideal for protecting computers, electrical equipment, and server rooms.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, ang Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082) ay \'Walang iniiwan na residue, kaya ito ay perpekto para sa pagprotekta sa mga computer, kagamitang de-kuryente, at server room.\'","choice_a_en":"Water Fire Extinguisher","choice_a_fil":"Water Fire Extinguisher","choice_b_en":"Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082)","choice_b_fil":"Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082)","choice_c_en":"Foam Fire Extinguisher","choice_c_fil":"Foam Fire Extinguisher","choice_d_en":"Dry Chemical Powder (ABC)","choice_d_fil":"Dry Chemical Powder (ABC)"},{"number":5,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"For which fire classes is a Foam Fire Extinguisher suitable?","question_fil":"Para sa anong mga uri ng sunog ang Foam Fire Extinguisher?","explanation_en":"The lesson indicates Foam Fire Extinguisher is \'Suitable for: Class A, Class B Fires.\'","explanation_fil":"Isinasaad ng aralin na ang Foam Fire Extinguisher ay \'Angkop para sa: Sunog ng Class A, Class B.\'","choice_a_en":"Class A only","choice_a_fil":"Class A lamang","choice_b_en":"Class B only","choice_b_fil":"Class B lamang","choice_c_en":"Class A and Class B","choice_c_fil":"Class A at Class B","choice_d_en":"Class A, Class B, and Class C","choice_d_fil":"Class A, Class B, at Class C"},{"number":6,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"Before using a fire extinguisher, what is one crucial question you should ask yourself regarding your safety?","question_fil":"Bago gamitin ang isang fire extinguisher, ano ang isang mahalagang tanong na dapat mong itanong sa iyong sarili tungkol sa iyong kaligtasan?","explanation_en":"The \'Before Using a Fire Extinguisher\' section lists: \'\\u2714 Is there a clear escape route behind you?\'","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa seksyong \'Bago Gamitin ang Fire Extinguisher\': \'\\u2714 May malinaw ba na ruta ng pagtakas sa iyong likuran?\'","choice_a_en":"Is the extinguisher fully charged?","choice_a_fil":"Puno ba ang charge ng extinguisher?","choice_b_en":"Is there a clear escape route behind you?","choice_b_fil":"May malinaw ba na ruta ng pagtakas sa iyong likuran?","choice_c_en":"Have all valuables been secured?","choice_c_fil":"Nai-secure na ba ang lahat ng mahahalagang bagay?","choice_d_en":"Is the fire alarm system functioning properly?","choice_d_fil":"Gumagana ba nang maayos ang fire alarm system?"},{"number":7,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"When should immediate evacuation be considered the safest option, according to the lesson?","question_fil":"Kailan dapat ituring na pinakaligtas na opsyon ang agarang paglikas, ayon sa aralin?","explanation_en":"The \'Why Fire Extinguishers are Important\' section states: \'if the fire grows rapidly, spreads to multiple areas, or produces excessive smoke, personal safety should always take priority over firefighting.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa seksyong \'Bakit Mahalaga ang Fire Extinguisher\': \'kung mabilis na lumalaki ang sunog, kumakalat sa maraming lugar, o naglalabas ng labis na usok, laging dapat unahin ang personal na kaligtasan kaysa sa pagpatay ng sunog.\'","choice_a_en":"If the fire alarm has not yet been activated.","choice_a_fil":"Kung hindi pa naaktibo ang fire alarm.","choice_b_en":"If you are unsure of the fire extinguisher\'s expiration date.","choice_b_fil":"Kung hindi ka sigurado sa expiration date ng fire extinguisher.","choice_c_en":"If the fire grows rapidly, spreads, or produces excessive smoke.","choice_c_fil":"Kung mabilis na lumalaki ang sunog, kumakalat, o naglalabas ng labis na usok.","choice_d_en":"If emergency responders have not yet arrived on the scene.","choice_d_fil":"Kung hindi pa nakarating ang mga emergency responder sa pinangyarihan."},{"number":8,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"What does the \'P\' in the PASS Technique stand for?","question_fil":"Ano ang ibig sabihin ng \'P\' sa Teknikong PASS?","explanation_en":"The PASS Technique section clearly states: \'P \\u2014 Pull the Pin\'.","explanation_fil":"Malinaw na nakasaad sa seksyon ng Teknikong PASS: \'P \\u2014 Pull the Pin\'.","choice_a_en":"Point","choice_a_fil":"Point","choice_b_en":"Prevent","choice_b_fil":"Prevent","choice_c_en":"Pull","choice_c_fil":"Pull","choice_d_en":"Protect","choice_d_fil":"Protect"},{"number":9,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"When performing the \'Aim\' step of the PASS Technique, where should the nozzle be directed?","question_fil":"Kapag ginagawa ang hakbang na \'Aim\' (Itutok) ng Teknikong PASS, saan dapat itutok ang nozzle?","explanation_en":"The lesson states for \'Aim\': \'Aim the nozzle at the base of the fire, not at the flames.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa aralin para sa \'Aim\': \'Itutok ang nozzle sa paanan ng apoy, hindi sa mismong ningas.\'","choice_a_en":"Directly at the center of the flames.","choice_a_fil":"Direkta sa gitna ng apoy.","choice_b_en":"At the top of the smoke plume.","choice_b_fil":"Sa itaas ng usok.","choice_c_en":"At the base of the fire.","choice_c_fil":"Sa paanan ng apoy.","choice_d_en":"Towards the ceiling to allow the agent to fall.","choice_d_fil":"Pataas sa kisame upang bumagsak ang ahente."},{"number":10,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"During the \'Sweep\' step of the PASS Technique, how should the nozzle be moved?","question_fil":"Sa hakbang na \'Sweep\' (Walisan) ng Teknikong PASS, paano dapat igalaw ang nozzle?","explanation_en":"The lesson states for \'Sweep\': \'Move the nozzle slowly from side to side while aiming at the base of the fire until it is completely extinguished.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa aralin para sa \'Sweep\': \'Igalaw ang nozzle nang dahan-dahan mula sa gilid patungo sa kabilang gilid habang itinatarget ang paanan ng apoy hanggang sa ito ay tuluyang maapula.\'","choice_a_en":"In a circular motion around the fire.","choice_a_fil":"Sa pabilog na galaw sa paligid ng apoy.","choice_b_en":"Quickly up and down the flames.","choice_b_fil":"Mabilis na pataas at pababa sa apoy.","choice_c_en":"Slowly from side to side at the base of the fire.","choice_c_fil":"Dahan-dahan mula sa gilid patungo sa kabilang gilid sa paanan ng apoy.","choice_d_en":"Towards the nearest exit.","choice_d_fil":"Patungo sa pinakamalapit na labasan."},{"number":11,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which of the following is an important safety reminder when fighting a fire with an extinguisher?","question_fil":"Alin sa sumusunod ang mahalagang paalala sa kaligtasan kapag nilalabanan ang sunog gamit ang fire extinguisher?","explanation_en":"The \'Important Safety Reminders\' section lists: \'Always keep an exit behind you.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa seksyong \'Mahahalagang Paalala sa Kaligtasan\': \'Laging siguraduhin na may labasan sa iyong likuran.\'","choice_a_en":"Always turn your back on the fire to protect your eyes.","choice_a_fil":"Palaging talikuran ang apoy upang protektahan ang iyong mga mata.","choice_b_en":"Stand as close as possible to ensure accuracy.","choice_b_fil":"Tumayo nang napakalapit hangga\'t maaari upang matiyak ang pagiging tumpak.","choice_c_en":"Always keep an exit behind you.","choice_c_fil":"Laging siguraduhin na may labasan sa iyong likuran.","choice_d_en":"Continue fighting the fire even if it spreads rapidly.","choice_d_fil":"Ipagpatuloy ang paglaban sa sunog kahit pa mabilis itong kumalat."},{"number":12,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"What should you do immediately if smoke becomes excessive while attempting to extinguish a fire?","question_fil":"Ano ang dapat mong agad na gawin kung labis na ang usok habang sinusubukang apulahin ang sunog?","explanation_en":"The \'Important Safety Reminders\' section advises: \'Leave the area immediately if smoke becomes excessive.\'","explanation_fil":"Ang seksyong \'Mahahalagang Paalala sa Kaligtasan\' ay nagpapayo: \'Agad na umalis sa lugar kung labis na ang usok.\'","choice_a_en":"Try to locate the source of the excessive smoke.","choice_a_fil":"Subukang hanapin ang pinagmulan ng labis na usok.","choice_b_en":"Continue fighting the fire while crouching low.","choice_b_fil":"Ipagpatuloy ang paglaban sa sunog habang nakayuko.","choice_c_en":"Leave the area immediately.","choice_c_fil":"Agad na umalis sa lugar.","choice_d_en":"Use a different type of extinguisher.","choice_d_fil":"Gumamit ng ibang uri ng extinguisher."},{"number":13,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which class of fire involves ordinary combustible materials like wood, paper, and cloth?","question_fil":"Aling klase ng sunog ang kinasasangkutan ng karaniwang nasusunog na materyales tulad ng kahoy, papel, at tela?","explanation_en":"Under Water Fire Extinguisher, it says \'Suitable for: Class A Fires Examples: Wood Paper Cloth Cardboard.\'","explanation_fil":"Sa ilalim ng Water Fire Extinguisher, nakasaad: \'Angkop para sa: Class A na Sunog Halimbawa: Kahoy, Papel, Tela, Karton.\'","choice_a_en":"Class B","choice_a_fil":"Class B","choice_b_en":"Class C","choice_b_fil":"Class C","choice_c_en":"Class A","choice_c_fil":"Class A","choice_d_en":"Class D","choice_d_fil":"Class D"},{"number":14,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"According to the lesson, what is a common mistake to avoid when using a fire extinguisher?","question_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, ano ang karaniwang pagkakamali na dapat iwasan kapag gumagamit ng fire extinguisher?","explanation_en":"The \'Common Mistakes\' section lists: \'Standing too close to the fire.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa seksyong \'Karaniwang Pagkakamali\': \'Pagiging masyadong malapit sa sunog.\'","choice_a_en":"Activating the fire alarm before using the extinguisher.","choice_a_fil":"Pag-aktibo ng fire alarm bago gamitin ang extinguisher.","choice_b_en":"Aiming at the base of the fire.","choice_b_fil":"Pag-itutok sa paanan ng apoy.","choice_c_en":"Standing too close to the fire.","choice_c_fil":"Pagiging masyadong malapit sa sunog.","choice_d_en":"Notifying emergency responders after extinguishing the fire.","choice_d_fil":"Pagpapaalam sa mga emergency responder pagkatapos maapula ang sunog."},{"number":15,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"If the answer to any of the questions in the \'Before Using a Fire Extinguisher\' checklist is \'No,\' what is the recommended action?","question_fil":"Kung ang sagot sa alinman sa mga tanong sa checklist na \'Bago Gamitin ang Fire Extinguisher\' ay \'Hindi,\' ano ang inirerekomendang aksyon?","explanation_en":"The lesson states: \'If the answer to any of these questions is No, evacuate immediately instead of attempting to fight the fire.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa aralin: \'Kung ang sagot sa alinman sa mga tanong na ito ay Hindi, agad na lumikas sa halip na subukang labanan ang sunog.\'","choice_a_en":"Proceed with caution and use the extinguisher.","choice_a_fil":"Magpatuloy nang may pag-iingat at gamitin ang extinguisher.","choice_b_en":"Find someone else to fight the fire.","choice_b_fil":"Humanap ng iba na lalaban sa sunog.","choice_c_en":"Evacuate immediately.","choice_c_fil":"Agad na lumikas.","choice_d_en":"Activate the fire alarm if not already done.","choice_d_fil":"I-aktibo ang fire alarm kung hindi pa nagawa."},{"number":16,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which of the following is listed as a learning objective for this lesson?","question_fil":"Alin sa sumusunod ang nakalista bilang layunin ng pagkatuto para sa araling ito?","explanation_en":"One of the Learning Objectives is: \'Recognize situations where using a fire extinguisher is appropriate.\'","explanation_fil":"Isa sa mga Layunin ng Pagkatuto ay: \'Makilala ang mga sitwasyon kung saan angkop ang paggamit ng fire extinguisher.\'","choice_a_en":"To identify the maximum range of different fire extinguishers.","choice_a_fil":"Upang matukoy ang pinakamataas na abot ng iba\'t ibang fire extinguisher.","choice_b_en":"To demonstrate advanced fire suppression techniques.","choice_b_fil":"Upang ipakita ang mga advanced na teknik sa pag-apula ng sunog.","choice_c_en":"To recognize situations where using a fire extinguisher is appropriate.","choice_c_fil":"Upang makilala ang mga sitwasyon kung saan angkop ang paggamit ng fire extinguisher.","choice_d_en":"To perform routine maintenance on fire extinguishers.","choice_d_fil":"Upang magsagawa ng regular na pagpapanatili sa mga fire extinguisher."},{"number":17,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"After successfully extinguishing a fire using the PASS technique, what immediate action is advised?","question_fil":"Matapos matagumpay na maapula ang sunog gamit ang Teknikong PASS, ano ang agarang aksyon na ipinapayo?","explanation_en":"The \'Sweep\' step of the PASS Technique states: \'Continue observing the area in case the fire reignites.\'","explanation_fil":"Ang hakbang na \'Sweep\' (Walisan) ng Teknikong PASS ay nagsasaad: \'Patuloy na obserbahan ang lugar kung sakaling muling magliyab ang apoy.\'","choice_a_en":"Store the extinguisher back in its place.","choice_a_fil":"Ibalik ang extinguisher sa lalagyan nito.","choice_b_en":"Turn your back on the area and leave.","choice_b_fil":"Talikuran ang lugar at umalis.","choice_c_en":"Continue observing the area in case the fire reignites.","choice_c_fil":"Patuloy na obserbahan ang lugar kung sakaling muling magliyab ang apoy.","choice_d_en":"Immediately report the incident to local media.","choice_d_fil":"Agad na iulat ang insidente sa lokal na media."},{"number":18,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"Which of these is explicitly listed as a safety reminder to avoid?","question_fil":"Alin sa mga ito ang tahasang nakalista bilang paalala sa kaligtasan na dapat iwasan?","explanation_en":"The \'Important Safety Reminders\' section includes: \'Never use water on electrical fires.\' Options A, C, D are implied or relate to other points, but B is a direct \'never\' statement.","explanation_fil":"Kasama sa seksyong \'Mahahalagang Paalala sa Kaligtasan\': \'Huwag na huwag gumamit ng tubig sa sunog na dulot ng kuryente.\' Ang mga opsyon A, C, D ay ipinahiwatig o may kaugnayan sa ibang punto, ngunit ang B ay isang direktang pahayag na \'huwag na huwag\'.","choice_a_en":"Standing too far from the fire.","choice_a_fil":"Pagiging masyadong malayo sa sunog.","choice_b_en":"Never using water on electrical fires.","choice_b_fil":"Huwag na huwag gumamit ng tubig sa sunog na dulot ng kuryente.","choice_c_en":"Activating the fire alarm late.","choice_c_fil":"Huling pag-aktibo ng fire alarm.","choice_d_en":"Not having an escape route.","choice_d_fil":"Walang ruta ng pagtakas."},{"number":19,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"What characteristic makes Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082) extinguishers suitable for server rooms?","question_fil":"Anong katangian ang nagpapaging angkop sa mga Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082) extinguisher para sa mga server room?","explanation_en":"The content states: \'Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082) ... Leaves no residue, making it ideal for protecting computers, electrical equipment, and server rooms.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa nilalaman: \'Carbon Dioxide (CO\\u2082) ... Walang iniiwan na residue, kaya ito ay perpekto para sa pagprotekta sa mga computer, kagamitang de-kuryente, at server room.\'","choice_a_en":"Their ability to cool burning materials effectively.","choice_a_fil":"Ang kanilang kakayahang palamigin nang epektibo ang mga nasusunog na materyales.","choice_b_en":"Their effectiveness against Class A fires.","choice_b_fil":"Ang kanilang pagiging epektibo laban sa Class A na sunog.","choice_c_en":"The fact that they leave no residue.","choice_c_fil":"Ang katotohanang wala silang iniiwan na residue.","choice_d_en":"Their suitability for flammable liquid fires only.","choice_d_fil":"Ang kanilang pagiging angkop para sa sunog ng nasusunog na likido lamang."},{"number":20,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"According to the lesson, when does personal safety take priority over firefighting?","question_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, kailan dapat unahin ang personal na kaligtasan kaysa sa paglaban sa sunog?","explanation_en":"The lesson states: \'if the fire grows rapidly, spreads to multiple areas, or produces excessive smoke, personal safety should always take priority over firefighting.\'","explanation_fil":"Ayon sa aralin: \'kung mabilis na lumalaki ang sunog, kumakalat sa maraming lugar, o naglalabas ng labis na usok, laging dapat unahin ang personal na kaligtasan kaysa sa paglaban sa sunog.\'","choice_a_en":"Only when you don\'t know the PASS technique.","choice_a_fil":"Kapag hindi mo lang alam ang Teknikong PASS.","choice_b_en":"When the fire is small but producing some smoke.","choice_b_fil":"Kapag maliit ang sunog ngunit naglalabas ng kaunting usok.","choice_c_en":"If the fire grows rapidly, spreads, or produces excessive smoke.","choice_c_fil":"Kung mabilis na lumalaki ang sunog, kumakalat, o naglalabas ng labis na usok.","choice_d_en":"After emergency responders have arrived and taken over.","choice_d_fil":"Pagkatapos dumating at mangasiwa ang mga emergency responder."}]', 'en', '{"en":{"status":"published","outdated":false,"published_at":"2026-07-17T00:09:11+08:00"},"fil":{"status":"draft","outdated":false,"translated_at":"2026-07-17T00:05:45+08:00"}}', 'AI Generated', NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, '2026-07-16 16:09:11', 3, 3, '2026-07-16 16:05:45', '2026-07-16 16:04:59', '2026-07-16 16:09:11'),
	(7, 7, 1, 'published', '[{"number":1,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"What is the primary definition of first aid according to the lesson?","question_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, ano ang pangunahing kahulugan ng unang lunas?","explanation_en":"The lesson defines first aid as \'the immediate care provided to an injured or ill person before professional medical help arrives.\'","explanation_fil":"Binibigyang kahulugan ng aralin ang unang lunas bilang \'ang agad na pangangalaga na ibinibigay sa isang taong nasugatan o nagkasakit bago dumating ang propesyonal na tulong medikal.\'","choice_a_en":"Professional medical treatment provided in a hospital.","choice_a_fil":"Propesyonal na paggamot medikal na ibinibigay sa isang ospital.","choice_b_en":"Immediate care provided to an injured or ill person before professional medical help arrives.","choice_b_fil":"Agad na pangangalaga na ibinibigay sa isang taong nasugatan o nagkasakit bago dumating ang propesyonal na tulong medikal.","choice_c_en":"Long-term rehabilitation for fire-related injuries.","choice_c_fil":"Pangmatagalang rehabilitasyon para sa mga pinsalang dulot ng sunog.","choice_d_en":"The process of calling emergency services only.","choice_d_fil":"Ang proseso ng pagtawag lamang sa mga serbisyong pang-emergency."},{"number":2,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"D","question_en":"Which of the following is NOT listed as a goal of first aid?","question_fil":"Alin sa mga sumusunod ang HINDI nakalista bilang layunin ng unang lunas?","explanation_en":"The goals of first aid are to preserve life, prevent injury from worsening, and promote recovery. Diagnosing the exact cause is not listed.","explanation_fil":"Ang mga layunin ng unang lunas ay panatilihin ang buhay, pigilan ang paglala ng pinsala, at itaguyod ang paggaling. Hindi nakalista ang pagsusuri sa eksaktong sanhi.","choice_a_en":"Preserve life.","choice_a_fil":"Panatilihin ang buhay.","choice_b_en":"Promote recovery.","choice_b_fil":"Itaguyod ang paggaling.","choice_c_en":"Prevent the injury from becoming worse.","choice_c_fil":"Pigilan ang paglala ng pinsala.","choice_d_en":"Diagnose the exact cause of injury.","choice_d_fil":"Suriin ang eksaktong sanhi ng pinsala."},{"number":3,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which of the following is listed as a common fire-related injury?","question_fil":"Alin sa mga sumusunod ang nakalista bilang karaniwang pinsala na dulot ng sunog?","explanation_en":"The lesson lists \'Heat exhaustion\' as one of the common fire-related injuries.","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa aralin ang \'Pagkapagod sa init (Heat exhaustion)\' bilang isa sa mga karaniwang pinsala na dulot ng sunog.","choice_a_en":"Allergic reactions.","choice_a_fil":"Mga reaksyong alerhiya.","choice_b_en":"Sprained ankles.","choice_b_fil":"Pilay sa bukung-bukong.","choice_c_en":"Heat exhaustion.","choice_c_fil":"Pagkapagod sa init (Heat exhaustion).","choice_d_en":"Food poisoning.","choice_d_fil":"Pagkalason sa pagkain."},{"number":4,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"What is the immediate first step for treating minor burns, according to the lesson?","question_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, ano ang agad na unang hakbang sa paggamot ng mga minor na paso?","explanation_en":"For minor burns, the first step is to \'Move the victim away from the heat source.\'","explanation_fil":"Para sa mga minor na paso, ang unang hakbang ay \'Ilipat ang biktima palayo sa pinagmulan ng init.\'","choice_a_en":"Apply butter to the burned area.","choice_a_fil":"Lagyan ng mantikilya ang napasong bahagi.","choice_b_en":"Move the victim away from the heat source.","choice_b_fil":"Ilipat ang biktima palayo sa pinagmulan ng init.","choice_c_en":"Pop any blisters that have formed.","choice_c_fil":"Pumutok ang anumang paltos na nabuo.","choice_d_en":"Cover the burn with a dry cloth.","choice_d_fil":"Takpan ang paso ng tuyong tela."},{"number":5,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"For how long should a minor burn be cooled under cool running water?","question_fil":"Gaano katagal dapat palamigin ang isang minor na paso sa ilalim ng malamig na tubig na umaagos?","explanation_en":"The lesson states, \'Cool the burned area under cool running water for at least 20 minutes.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin, \'Palamigin ang napasong bahagi sa ilalim ng malamig na tubig na umaagos nang hindi bababa sa 20 minuto.\'","choice_a_en":"5 minutes.","choice_a_fil":"5 minuto.","choice_b_en":"At least 10 minutes.","choice_b_fil":"Hindi bababa sa 10 minuto.","choice_c_en":"At least 20 minutes.","choice_c_fil":"Hindi bababa sa 20 minuto.","choice_d_en":"Until the pain stops completely.","choice_d_fil":"Hanggang sa tuluyang mawala ang sakit."},{"number":6,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"According to the lesson, which substance should NOT be applied to a minor burn?","question_fil":"Ayon sa aralin, aling substansya ang HINDI dapat ilagay sa isang minor na paso?","explanation_en":"The lesson explicitly states, \'Do not apply: Toothpaste, Butter, Ice, Cooking oil, Ointments unless advised by medical professionals.\'","explanation_fil":"Malinaw na nakasaad sa aralin, \'Huwag ilagay: Toothpaste, Mantikilya, Yelo, Mantika, Mga pamahid maliban kung ipinapayo ng mga propesyonal sa medisina.\'","choice_a_en":"Clean, sterile non-stick dressing.","choice_a_fil":"Malinis, isteril, hindi dumidikit na panakip.","choice_b_en":"Cool running water.","choice_b_fil":"Malamig na tubig na umaagos.","choice_c_en":"Toothpaste.","choice_c_fil":"Toothpaste.","choice_d_en":"An ointment, if advised by medical professionals.","choice_d_fil":"Isang pamahid, kung ipinapayo ng mga propesyonal sa medisina."},{"number":7,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which of the following is a common sign of smoke inhalation?","question_fil":"Alin sa mga sumusunod ang karaniwang tanda ng paglanghap ng usok?","explanation_en":"Common signs of smoke inhalation include \'Persistent coughing,\' difficulty breathing, dizziness, headache, black soot, and confusion.","explanation_fil":"Ang mga karaniwang tanda ng paglanghap ng usok ay kinabibilangan ng \'Patuloy na pag-ubo,\' hirap sa paghinga, pagkahilo, pananakit ng ulo, itim na uling, at pagkalito.","choice_a_en":"Clear skin with no visible soot.","choice_a_fil":"Malinaw na balat na walang nakikitang uling.","choice_b_en":"Increased energy and alertness.","choice_b_fil":"Pagtaas ng enerhiya at pagiging alisto.","choice_c_en":"Persistent coughing.","choice_c_fil":"Patuloy na pag-ubo.","choice_d_en":"Feeling overly warm.","choice_d_fil":"Pakiramdam ng sobrang init."},{"number":8,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"What is the immediate action to take for someone showing signs of smoke inhalation?","question_fil":"Ano ang agarang aksyon na dapat gawin para sa isang taong nagpapakita ng mga tanda ng paglanghap ng usok?","explanation_en":"The lesson states, \'Move the person to fresh air immediately and seek medical attention.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin, \'Ilipat agad ang tao sa sariwang hangin at humingi ng medikal na atensyon.\'","choice_a_en":"Give them a glass of water.","choice_a_fil":"Bigyan sila ng isang basong tubig.","choice_b_en":"Move the person to fresh air immediately and seek medical attention.","choice_b_fil":"Ilipat agad ang tao sa sariwang hangin at humingi ng medikal na atensyon.","choice_c_en":"Apply a cold compress to their forehead.","choice_c_fil":"Lagyan ng malamig na compress ang kanilang noo.","choice_d_en":"Cover their nose and mouth with a wet cloth and keep them in the smoky area.","choice_d_fil":"Takpan ang kanilang ilong at bibig ng basang tela at panatilihin sila sa mausok na lugar."},{"number":9,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Before giving first aid to an injured person, what is the most important step listed?","question_fil":"Bago magbigay ng unang lunas sa isang nasugatang tao, ano ang pinakamahalagang hakbang na nakalista?","explanation_en":"The lesson emphasizes, \'Before giving first aid: Ensure the area is safe. Protect yourself first.\'","explanation_fil":"Binibigyang-diin ng aralin, \'Bago magbigay ng unang lunas: Siguraduhin na ligtas ang lugar. Protektahan ang sarili muna.\'","choice_a_en":"Reassure the injured person.","choice_a_fil":"Panataghin ang nasugatang tao.","choice_b_en":"Stay calm.","choice_b_fil":"Manatiling kalmado.","choice_c_en":"Ensure the area is safe.","choice_c_fil":"Siguraduhin na ligtas ang lugar.","choice_d_en":"Call emergency responders immediately.","choice_d_fil":"Tumawag agad sa mga tagatugon sa emergency."},{"number":10,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"When should professional medical assistance be sought immediately during a fire emergency?","question_fil":"Kailan dapat agad humingi ng propesyonal na tulong medikal sa panahon ng isang emergency sa sunog?","explanation_en":"The lesson lists, \'Immediately seek professional medical assistance if: The fire involved chemicals or electricity.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakalista sa aralin, \'Agad humingi ng propesyonal na tulong medikal kung: Ang sunog ay kinasasangkutan ng mga kemikal o kuryente.\'","choice_a_en":"If the burn is very small.","choice_a_fil":"Kung napakaliit ng paso.","choice_b_en":"If the victim is only slightly confused.","choice_b_fil":"Kung bahagya lamang nalilito ang biktima.","choice_c_en":"If the fire involved chemicals or electricity.","choice_c_fil":"Kung ang sunog ay kinasasangkutan ng mga kemikal o kuryente.","choice_d_en":"If the victim feels a little dizzy but is otherwise fine.","choice_d_fil":"Kung ang biktima ay nakaramdam lamang ng bahagyang pagkahilo ngunit maayos naman."},{"number":11,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"A burn on which body part would immediately warrant professional medical assistance?","question_fil":"Ang paso sa aling bahagi ng katawan ang agarang nangangailangan ng propesyonal na tulong medikal?","explanation_en":"The lesson states to seek immediate medical assistance if \'Burns involve the face, hands, feet, or genitals.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin na humingi ng agarang tulong medikal kung \'Ang mga paso ay kinasasangkutan ng mukha, kamay, paa, o ari.\'","choice_a_en":"Forearm.","choice_a_fil":"Braso.","choice_b_en":"Thigh.","choice_b_fil":"Hita.","choice_c_en":"Foot.","choice_c_fil":"Paa.","choice_d_en":"Shoulder.","choice_d_fil":"Balikat."},{"number":12,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"Which action is listed as a common mistake to avoid in first aid during fire emergencies?","question_fil":"Aling aksyon ang nakalista bilang karaniwang pagkakamali na dapat iwasan sa unang lunas sa panahon ng emergency sa sunog?","explanation_en":"The lesson states, \'Do not: Pop blisters.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin, \'Huwag: Paputukin ang mga paltos.\'","choice_a_en":"Calling emergency responders.","choice_a_fil":"Pagtawag sa mga tagatugon sa emergency.","choice_b_en":"Covering a burn with a sterile dressing.","choice_b_fil":"Pagtatakip ng paso ng isteril na panakip.","choice_c_en":"Popping blisters.","choice_c_fil":"Pagpapaputok ng mga paltos.","choice_d_en":"Moving a victim away from a heat source.","choice_d_fil":"Paglilipat ng biktima palayo sa pinagmulan ng init."},{"number":13,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"What should NOT be delayed when dealing with fire-related injuries?","question_fil":"Ano ang HINDI dapat ipagpaliban kapag nakikitungo sa mga pinsalang dulot ng sunog?","explanation_en":"The lesson advises, \'Do not: Delay calling emergency responders.\'","explanation_fil":"Ipinapayo ng aralin, \'Huwag: Ipagpaliban ang pagtawag sa mga tagatugon sa emergency.\'","choice_a_en":"Cooling a minor burn.","choice_a_fil":"Pagpapalamig ng minor na paso.","choice_b_en":"Reassuring the injured person.","choice_b_fil":"Pagpapapanatag sa nasugatang tao.","choice_c_en":"Calling emergency responders for serious injuries.","choice_c_fil":"Pagtawag sa mga tagatugon sa emergency para sa malubhang pinsala.","choice_d_en":"Applying a sterile dressing.","choice_d_fil":"Paglalagay ng isteril na panakip."},{"number":14,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"B","question_en":"According to the lesson overview, providing proper first aid during the first few minutes after an incident can help reduce what?","question_fil":"Ayon sa pangkalahatang-ideya ng aralin, ang pagbibigay ng tamang unang lunas sa unang ilang minuto pagkatapos ng insidente ay makakatulong na mabawasan ang ano?","explanation_en":"The lesson overview states, \'Providing proper first aid during the first few minutes after an incident can help reduce the severity of injuries and improve the chances of recovery.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa pangkalahatang-ideya ng aralin, \'Ang pagbibigay ng tamang unang lunas sa unang ilang minuto pagkatapos ng insidente ay makakatulong na mabawasan ang kalubhaan ng mga pinsala at mapabuti ang pagkakataon ng paggaling.\'","choice_a_en":"The need for any professional medical help.","choice_a_fil":"Ang pangangailangan para sa anumang propesyonal na tulong medikal.","choice_b_en":"The severity of injuries and improve chances of recovery.","choice_b_fil":"Ang kalubhaan ng mga pinsala at mapabuti ang pagkakataon ng paggaling.","choice_c_en":"The amount of smoke in the area.","choice_c_fil":"Ang dami ng usok sa lugar.","choice_d_en":"The emotional impact on bystanders.","choice_d_fil":"Ang emosyonal na epekto sa mga nakasaksi."},{"number":15,"competency":"safety_awareness","correct_answer":"A","question_en":"What is highlighted as a key takeaway regarding safety?","question_fil":"Ano ang binibigyang-diin bilang isang mahalagang aral tungkol sa kaligtasan?","explanation_en":"One of the Key Takeaways is \'Always prioritize scene safety.\'","explanation_fil":"Isa sa mga Mahalagang Aral ay \'Laging unahin ang kaligtasan ng pinangyarihan.\'","choice_a_en":"Always prioritize scene safety.","choice_a_fil":"Laging unahin ang kaligtasan ng pinangyarihan.","choice_b_en":"Always move seriously injured victims.","choice_b_fil":"Laging ilipat ang mga biktima na malubhang nasugatan.","choice_c_en":"Always apply home remedies first.","choice_c_fil":"Laging gumamit muna ng mga panlunas na gawa sa bahay.","choice_d_en":"Always ignore minor breathing difficulties.","choice_d_fil":"Laging balewalain ang minor na hirap sa paghinga."},{"number":16,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"One of the learning objectives of this lesson is for participants to be able to identify what?","question_fil":"Isa sa mga layunin ng pagkatuto ng araling ito ay upang matukoy ng mga kalahok ang ano?","explanation_en":"A learning objective is \'Identify common injuries caused by fires.\'","explanation_fil":"Ang layunin ng pagkatuto ay \'Matukoy ang mga karaniwang pinsala na dulot ng sunog.\'","choice_a_en":"The chemical composition of smoke.","choice_a_fil":"Ang komposisyong kemikal ng usok.","choice_b_en":"Advanced surgical techniques for burns.","choice_b_fil":"Mga advanced na teknik ng operasyon para sa paso.","choice_c_en":"Common injuries caused by fires.","choice_c_fil":"Mga karaniwang pinsala na dulot ng sunog.","choice_d_en":"The exact temperature of a fire.","choice_d_fil":"Ang eksaktong temperatura ng apoy."},{"number":17,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"When should you immediately seek professional medical assistance regarding a burn victim?","question_fil":"Kailan dapat agad humingi ng propesyonal na tulong medikal tungkol sa isang biktima ng paso?","explanation_en":"The lesson states to \'Immediately seek professional medical assistance if: The victim loses consciousness.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin na \'Agad humingi ng propesyonal na tulong medikal kung: Ang biktima ay nawalan ng malay.\'","choice_a_en":"If the victim is conscious and responsive.","choice_a_fil":"Kung ang biktima ay may malay at tumutugon.","choice_b_en":"If the victim only has minor burns.","choice_b_fil":"Kung minor lamang ang paso ng biktima.","choice_c_en":"If the victim loses consciousness.","choice_c_fil":"Kung nawalan ng malay ang biktima.","choice_d_en":"If the victim can talk clearly.","choice_d_fil":"Kung malinaw na makapagsalita ang biktima."},{"number":18,"competency":"decision_making","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"After cooling a minor burn, what is the next recommended step from the lesson?","question_fil":"Pagkatapos palamigin ang isang minor na paso, ano ang susunod na inirerekomendang hakbang mula sa aralin?","explanation_en":"For minor burns, after cooling, the next step is to \'Cover the burn with a clean, sterile, non-stick dressing.\'","explanation_fil":"Para sa mga minor na paso, pagkatapos palamigin, ang susunod na hakbang ay \'Takpan ang paso ng malinis, isteril, hindi dumidikit na panakip.\'","choice_a_en":"Apply ice directly to the burn.","choice_a_fil":"Direktang lagyan ng yelo ang paso.","choice_b_en":"Leave the burn exposed to air.","choice_b_fil":"Iwanang nakalantad sa hangin ang paso.","choice_c_en":"Cover the burn with a clean, sterile, non-stick dressing.","choice_c_fil":"Takpan ang paso ng malinis, isteril, hindi dumidikit na panakip.","choice_d_en":"Rub the burn area vigorously.","choice_d_fil":"Kuskusin nang mariin ang bahaging napaso."},{"number":19,"competency":"knowledge","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"What specific action is mentioned as a common mistake to avoid regarding blisters?","question_fil":"Anong partikular na aksyon ang binanggit bilang karaniwang pagkakamali na dapat iwasan tungkol sa mga paltos?","explanation_en":"The lesson states, \'Do not: Pop blisters.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin, \'Huwag: Paputukin ang mga paltos.\'","choice_a_en":"Cool them with water.","choice_a_fil":"Palamigin ang mga ito ng tubig.","choice_b_en":"Cover them with a dressing.","choice_b_fil":"Takpan ang mga ito ng panakip.","choice_c_en":"Pop them.","choice_c_fil":"Paputukin ang mga ito.","choice_d_en":"Show them to a doctor.","choice_d_fil":"Ipakita ang mga ito sa doktor."},{"number":20,"competency":"emergency_response","correct_answer":"C","question_en":"If a person affected by fire has difficulty breathing, what is the recommended immediate action from the lesson?","question_fil":"Kung ang isang taong apektado ng sunog ay nahihirapang huminga, ano ang inirerekomendang agarang aksyon mula sa aralin?","explanation_en":"The lesson states, \'Immediately seek professional medical assistance if: The victim has difficulty breathing.\' Also, \'Do not: Ignore breathing difficulties.\'","explanation_fil":"Nakasaad sa aralin, \'Agad humingi ng propesyonal na tulong medikal kung: Ang biktima ay nahihirapan sa paghinga.\' Gayundin, \'Huwag: Balewalain ang hirap sa paghinga.\'","choice_a_en":"Ignore it and treat other injuries first.","choice_a_fil":"Balewalain ito at gamutin muna ang ibang pinsala.","choice_b_en":"Give them a warm drink.","choice_b_fil":"Bigyan sila ng mainit na inumin.","choice_c_en":"Immediately seek professional medical assistance.","choice_c_fil":"Agad humingi ng propesyonal na tulong medikal.","choice_d_en":"Ask them to hold their breath.","choice_d_fil":"Hilingin sa kanila na pigilin ang kanilang paghinga."}]', 'en', '{"en":{"status":"published","outdated":false,"published_at":"2026-07-18T22:26:16+08:00"},"fil":{"status":"draft","outdated":false,"translated_at":"2026-07-18T21:38:43+08:00"}}', 'AI Generated', NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, '2026-07-18 14:25:29', 3, 3, '2026-07-18 13:38:43', '2026-07-18 13:38:02', '2026-07-18 14:26:16');
